---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Thoughts on technology, development, and professional growth
bodyClass: blog-list-page
---

<div class="blog-list">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p class="blog-intro">Welcome to my blog where I share insights on technology, development practices, and lessons learned throughout my career.</p>

    {% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
            <article class="blog-post">
                <h2>
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
                </h2>
                <p class="post-meta">
                    <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">
                        {{ post.date | postDate }}
                    </time>
                    {% if post.data.tags %}
                        | Tags:
                        {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                            {% if tag != "post" %}
                                <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}
                    <span class="visitor-counter loading" data-path="{{ post.url }}">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"></path>
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="visitor-count">...</span>
                    </span>
                </p>
                {% if post.data.description %}
                    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more â†’</a>
            </article>
        {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
        <p>No blog posts yet. Check back soon!</p>
    {% endif %}
</div>